onent' is assigned a value but never used.","'FooterComponent' is assigned a value but never used.","'LoadingScreen' is assigned a value but never used.","'LoadingFooterScreen' is assigned a value but never used.","'LoadingCarDetailScreen' is assigned a value but never used.","'enquiriesArr' is assigned a value but never used.","eqeqeq","Expected '!==' and instead saw '!='.","BinaryExpression","unexpected","no-extra-bind","The function binding is unnecessary.","CallExpression",{"range":"726","text":"727"},"'selectedCar' is assigned a value but never used.","'setSelectedCar' is assigned a value but never used.","no-whitespace-before-property","Unexpected whitespace before property substring.","MemberExpression","unexpectedWhitespace",{"range":"728","text":"729"},"jsx-a11y/alt-text","img elements must have an alt prop, either with meaningful text, or an empty string for decorative images.","JSXOpeningElement","'showMessage' is assigned a value but never used.","'clearMessage' is assigned a value but never used.","react-hooks/exhaustive-deps","Assignments to the 'view' variable from inside React Hook useEffect will be lost after each render. To preserve the value over time, store it in a useRef Hook and keep the mutable value in the '.current' property. Otherwise, you can move this variable directly inside useEffect.","'message' is assigned a value but never used.","Expected '===' and instead saw '=='.","'createRef' is defined but never used.","'isLeaf' is assigned a value but never used.","'setMessage' is assigned a value but never used.",{"range":"730","text":"727"},"'axios' is defined but never used.","'GoogleOneTapLogin' is defined but never used.","'HeadersShopComponent' is assigned a value but never used.","'AppSidebarComponent' is assigned a value but never used.","React Hook useEffect has a missing dependency: 'isDesktop'. Either include it or remove the dependency array.","ArrayExpression",["731"],"'ViewShopsComponent' is assigned a value but never used.","'ge